WEBVTT

00:00:01.879 --> 00:00:04.718
[STUDENTS chatter]

00:00:05.010 --> 00:00:06.847
How did your mock exam go?

00:00:06.931 --> 00:00:08.433
Pretty well, I'd say.

00:00:09.520 --> 00:00:12.901
[KONO] I've had fun this year,
but I've also studied a lot.

00:00:12.984 --> 00:00:14.738
Such is the life of a senior.

00:00:15.531 --> 00:00:16.533
When I get home,

00:00:16.617 --> 00:00:18.746
I review my lessons
and old exam questions.

00:00:20.082 --> 00:00:21.000
In my spare time,

00:00:21.084 --> 00:00:23.338
I memorize vocabulary
and formulas.

00:00:24.925 --> 00:00:28.724
Though my daily grind is tough,
I do have a singular reprieve.

00:00:31.229 --> 00:00:32.774
And that's reading manga!

00:00:33.275 --> 00:00:34.861
The highlight of my whole week.

00:00:35.863 --> 00:00:37.784
Aah!

00:00:37.867 --> 00:00:39.328
[KONO]
He's a double agent?

00:00:39.412 --> 00:00:40.497
But, how?

00:00:40.581 --> 00:00:42.001
I never even saw it coming!

00:00:42.084 --> 00:00:43.713
Boy,
did this slice-of-life chapter

00:00:43.796 --> 00:00:44.756
take a turn!

00:00:45.508 --> 00:00:47.261
You're killing me!

00:00:47.344 --> 00:00:49.516
[groans]

00:00:50.100 --> 00:00:52.271
Next week can't come
soon enough!

00:02:25.708 --> 00:02:27.545
[STUDENTS chatter]

00:02:28.254 --> 00:02:30.300
-[rustling]
-[zipping]

00:02:30.383 --> 00:02:32.054
Mm. [giggles]

00:02:32.639 --> 00:02:33.849
[AYASAKI]
Someone's sure in a good mood!

00:02:33.933 --> 00:02:34.768
[chuckles]

00:02:35.435 --> 00:02:36.855
[KONO]
I'm happy to be heading home!

00:02:38.776 --> 00:02:40.320
[KONO]
Konoha's new chapter!

00:02:40.403 --> 00:02:42.324
Konoha's new chapter!

00:02:42.407 --> 00:02:44.328
Konoha's new chapter!

00:02:44.411 --> 00:02:46.332
Konoha's new chapter!

00:02:46.415 --> 00:02:48.294
Konoha's new chapter!

00:02:48.378 --> 00:02:50.215
Konoha's new chapter!

00:02:55.183 --> 00:02:56.937
-Um, pardon me.
-Hm?

00:02:57.020 --> 00:02:59.066
Did the latest <i>Weekly Shinobi</i>
come in today?

00:02:59.149 --> 00:03:00.443
Uh, yeah.

00:03:01.320 --> 00:03:03.157
We sold out of it
a few minutes ago.

00:03:03.659 --> 00:03:06.080
[whimpers]

00:03:07.040 --> 00:03:08.502
[MALE EMPLOYEE 207A]
Want to backorder one?

00:03:08.586 --> 00:03:10.088
Uh-uh.

00:03:11.508 --> 00:03:14.305
[KONO] Convenience stores
always sell out on release day,

00:03:14.388 --> 00:03:15.432
but even the bookstore

00:03:15.516 --> 00:03:18.564
didn't have
Konoha's new chapter.

00:03:22.739 --> 00:03:23.616
Why?

00:03:23.699 --> 00:03:25.536
After thinking
about Konoha all day,

00:03:25.620 --> 00:03:27.832
I might just die
from this disappointment!

00:03:27.915 --> 00:03:29.669
[YANAGI]
Huh? That you, Kono?

00:03:29.753 --> 00:03:30.588
[gasps]

00:03:31.590 --> 00:03:33.594
Oh! Yep! It sure is!

00:03:33.677 --> 00:03:34.721
Hey there.

00:03:34.804 --> 00:03:37.100
[KONO]
He witnessed my cringiness.

00:03:37.184 --> 00:03:39.564
So, you came here
for the latest <i>Weekly Shinobi?</i>

00:03:39.648 --> 00:03:41.860
Hm? Are you psychic
or something?

00:03:41.943 --> 00:03:42.779
Don't I wish!

00:03:42.862 --> 00:03:44.991
I heard you say
"Konoha's new chapter."

00:03:45.075 --> 00:03:47.120
-And you sounded upset.
-Ah!

00:03:48.832 --> 00:03:50.293
[KONO]
How embarrassing.

00:03:50.377 --> 00:03:52.632
[YANAGI]
Um, you can have mine,

00:03:52.715 --> 00:03:53.759
-if you'd like.
-[gasps]

00:03:55.638 --> 00:03:57.224
[YANAGI] Hasn't even been
cracked open yet.

00:03:58.226 --> 00:04:00.063
[gasps] I can't.

00:04:00.146 --> 00:04:00.981
Why?

00:04:01.065 --> 00:04:02.652
If you're fretting
because you're worried about me,

00:04:02.735 --> 00:04:03.779
please don't.

00:04:03.862 --> 00:04:04.948
I'll be fine.

00:04:05.031 --> 00:04:07.537
Doubt I would've bought it
if it hadn't been the last copy.

00:04:08.037 --> 00:04:09.582
I just came in here
to kill some time

00:04:09.666 --> 00:04:10.835
until my bus arrives.

00:04:12.003 --> 00:04:14.759
There are lots of bookstores
near the station by my house.

00:04:14.843 --> 00:04:16.680
-They can't all be sold out.
-[awed]

00:04:17.264 --> 00:04:18.307
Sorry to cut this short,

00:04:18.391 --> 00:04:19.936
but I should go
before I miss my bus.

00:04:20.019 --> 00:04:21.732
Wow! Thanks a million!

00:04:22.525 --> 00:04:24.403
I'll pay you back
first thing tomorrow!

00:04:24.988 --> 00:04:26.157
You are so cool.

00:04:26.240 --> 00:04:27.200
And kind.

00:04:27.284 --> 00:04:31.208
The way you helped me out,
you're just like Kaoru!

00:04:31.292 --> 00:04:35.718
♪

00:04:36.427 --> 00:04:38.849
Thank you very much. [chuckles]

00:04:38.932 --> 00:04:40.226
[KONO]
Awkward!

00:04:40.310 --> 00:04:42.147
Did comparing him
to one of the characters

00:04:42.230 --> 00:04:43.734
rub him the wrong way?

00:04:43.817 --> 00:04:45.529
Why'd I even open my mouth?

00:04:49.829 --> 00:04:50.998
♪

00:04:51.081 --> 00:04:53.085
[YANAGI] I remind her
of a fictional lady!

00:04:53.796 --> 00:04:54.631
Did she say that

00:04:54.714 --> 00:04:56.008
because she thinks
I'm effeminate?

00:04:56.551 --> 00:04:57.929
Oh, man.

00:04:58.680 --> 00:05:02.187
[KONO] I weirded him out
with silly fangirl nonsense.

00:05:02.688 --> 00:05:03.524
But...

00:05:10.996 --> 00:05:13.459
[KONO] I guess Yanagi's a fan
in his own right.

00:05:17.217 --> 00:05:19.639
-[footsteps]
-[YANAGI] Kono!

00:05:20.140 --> 00:05:22.018
Huh? Ah! Yanagi.

00:05:22.854 --> 00:05:23.689
Going to the bookstore,

00:05:23.772 --> 00:05:25.024
-I take it?
-Mm-hm!

00:05:25.108 --> 00:05:26.695
[KONO, YANAGI]
It's <i>Weekly Shinobi</i> release day

00:05:26.778 --> 00:05:27.738
today!

00:05:27.822 --> 00:05:29.032
[KONO, YANAGI chuckle]

00:05:30.828 --> 00:05:32.957
[KONO] Konoha's been
so exciting lately.

00:05:33.040 --> 00:05:34.376
I can't put it down!

00:05:34.459 --> 00:05:35.921
[YANAGI]
I can't blame you.

00:05:36.005 --> 00:05:38.426
Normally, I'll wait
for the full book publication.

00:05:38.510 --> 00:05:40.305
But once I read a manga
in a magazine,

00:05:40.388 --> 00:05:42.100
patience gives way to curiosity.

00:05:42.184 --> 00:05:44.981
[KONO] Every time!
Talk about an odd pair.

00:05:45.064 --> 00:05:46.192
[FEMALE STUDENTS laugh]

00:05:47.110 --> 00:05:49.072
[KONO]
Haven't heard that in a while!

00:05:49.156 --> 00:05:51.578
No one makes those comments
when I'm with Hori's group.

00:05:53.039 --> 00:05:55.502
-Maybe arm's length?
-[YANAGI gasps]

00:05:55.586 --> 00:05:56.796
Are you upset with me?

00:05:56.880 --> 00:05:57.757
[KONO]
No! Not at all!

00:05:57.840 --> 00:05:58.884
It's just, uh...

00:05:59.844 --> 00:06:01.890
When I'm by you,
girls get jealous.

00:06:01.973 --> 00:06:03.017
They just can't fathom

00:06:03.100 --> 00:06:04.812
why on earth
you'd spend time with me.

00:06:04.896 --> 00:06:05.773
[chuckles]

00:06:06.524 --> 00:06:07.359
Hm?

00:06:07.860 --> 00:06:09.071
And why is that?

00:06:09.948 --> 00:06:11.826
[KONO] Because you're cool,
and I'm not.

00:06:13.037 --> 00:06:14.498
[YANAGI]
"Cool"?

00:06:14.582 --> 00:06:15.416
-[AYASAKI whines]
-Huh.

00:06:15.501 --> 00:06:17.630
Remi got a nasty paper cut!

00:06:17.713 --> 00:06:19.634
Try thinking
about something fun.

00:06:19.717 --> 00:06:21.554
Like how school gets out
early today!

00:06:21.638 --> 00:06:23.558
Yay! [giggles]

00:06:23.642 --> 00:06:24.644
[KONO]
It's gone now.

00:06:24.727 --> 00:06:26.690
Don't cry
over a harmless little bug.

00:06:26.773 --> 00:06:28.527
I'm not crying.

00:06:28.610 --> 00:06:30.321
But, it's really gone?

00:06:30.405 --> 00:06:31.240
You're sure?

00:06:31.323 --> 00:06:32.910
You're cooler than me by far.

00:06:32.994 --> 00:06:33.954
[KONO]
Wait. What?

00:06:34.872 --> 00:06:36.166
You're not serious, are you?

00:06:36.250 --> 00:06:37.586
Because I think
everyone would agree

00:06:37.670 --> 00:06:38.964
you're way cooler.

00:06:39.047 --> 00:06:40.592
No,
I'd definitely want you around

00:06:40.676 --> 00:06:42.387
if I got hurt or scared.
[whimpers]

00:06:42.470 --> 00:06:43.724
How is that relevant?

00:06:44.892 --> 00:06:47.230
[KONO] It doesn't detract
from his coolness,

00:06:47.313 --> 00:06:48.692
but he is strange.

00:06:48.775 --> 00:06:50.194
[YANAGI]
Paper cuts stink.

00:06:50.278 --> 00:06:51.573
[KONO]
And I'd rather be described

00:06:51.656 --> 00:06:53.409
with other adjectives,
anyway, like...

00:06:54.161 --> 00:06:55.371
Cute would be nice.

00:06:57.167 --> 00:06:58.002
[KONO]
I noticed

00:06:58.085 --> 00:06:59.714
you haven't been wearing
your glasses lately.

00:06:59.797 --> 00:07:00.799
[YANAGI]
Yeah.

00:07:00.883 --> 00:07:02.302
They don't look all that good
on me.

00:07:03.304 --> 00:07:04.807
So, I've switched to contacts.

00:07:05.809 --> 00:07:07.521
[KONO]
I bet everything looks stunning

00:07:07.605 --> 00:07:08.982
on that gorgeous face!

00:07:09.066 --> 00:07:11.738
If I had a different style,
I might wear them more often.

00:07:11.821 --> 00:07:13.909
Maybe I'll check out frames
after the bookstore.

00:07:13.992 --> 00:07:16.664
[KONO] His delicate features
make mine look so homely!

00:07:16.748 --> 00:07:18.000
More than usual.

00:07:18.084 --> 00:07:20.088
[YANAGI] You're welcome
to go along with me.

00:07:20.171 --> 00:07:21.508
Huh? Go where?

00:07:21.591 --> 00:07:22.760
To look at new frames.

00:07:22.843 --> 00:07:23.929
New frames? Huh?

00:07:24.471 --> 00:07:25.766
You really want me along?

00:07:25.849 --> 00:07:27.603
Yes. If you aren't busy,
of course.

00:07:27.686 --> 00:07:28.855
No! I'll come!

00:07:29.481 --> 00:07:31.443
[KONO]
He asked so casually.

00:07:31.528 --> 00:07:35.159
Who could possibly turn down
such a charming invitation?

00:07:35.243 --> 00:07:36.579
Hm? Hey.

00:07:37.832 --> 00:07:39.669
I just thought
of a funny coincidence.

00:07:40.336 --> 00:07:41.255
Hm?

00:07:41.338 --> 00:07:42.800
Not that it means something,

00:07:42.883 --> 00:07:44.595
but our names
are kinds of trees.

00:07:44.679 --> 00:07:46.558
Right? "Yanagi" and "Sakura."

00:07:47.350 --> 00:07:48.185
[KONO]
Huh?

00:07:50.691 --> 00:07:54.030
♪

00:07:54.114 --> 00:07:55.909
[KONO]
No more!

00:07:55.993 --> 00:07:56.953
[YANAGI]
Kono, wait!

00:07:57.036 --> 00:07:58.289
Why are you running?

00:07:58.372 --> 00:07:59.876
Do you think
they're going to sell out?

00:08:02.715 --> 00:08:04.719
[KONO]
Everything does look stunning.

00:08:05.888 --> 00:08:07.808
Boy meets girl, boy likes girl,

00:08:07.892 --> 00:08:09.812
then boy and girl swap bodies!

00:08:09.896 --> 00:08:11.858
Ooh, I know that plotline.

00:08:11.941 --> 00:08:14.070
Yeah,
I read this novel ages ago!

00:08:14.154 --> 00:08:15.114
It is such a page-turner!

00:08:15.198 --> 00:08:16.408
-Uh, excuse me?
-What's it called?

00:08:16.491 --> 00:08:18.204
<i>-I'm Her and She's Me.</i>
-Posture, Yoshikawa.

00:08:18.287 --> 00:08:19.916
Has a TV show and everything.

00:08:19.999 --> 00:08:22.128
Huh?
That's first I've heard of it.

00:08:22.212 --> 00:08:24.007
[YOSHIKAWA]
What if Hori and Miyamura

00:08:24.090 --> 00:08:25.552
swapped bodies?

00:08:28.307 --> 00:08:29.685
Toru,
pull your head out of your butt

00:08:29.769 --> 00:08:30.854
and talk sense!

00:08:30.938 --> 00:08:32.482
Aw, come on.

00:08:32.566 --> 00:08:34.444
-Aw!
-[ISHIKAWA] Did she break?

00:08:34.528 --> 00:08:35.697
[SENGOKU]
Hey!

00:08:35.781 --> 00:08:38.285
Someone left their pencil case
back in the council room.

00:08:38.369 --> 00:08:39.872
Huh? Shu, most likely.

00:08:40.414 --> 00:08:42.126
Missing pencil case.

00:08:43.838 --> 00:08:46.928
[laughs] Classic Ishikawa!

00:08:47.011 --> 00:08:48.389
[sighs] Pipe down.

00:08:48.472 --> 00:08:50.644
-You're annoyingly loud.
-[cackling]

00:08:50.727 --> 00:08:52.021
-[cackling]
-What the heck?

00:08:52.105 --> 00:08:53.232
-[AYASAKI] Oh, Sengoku!
-Hm?

00:08:53.315 --> 00:08:54.610
[AYASAKI]
There you are!

00:08:54.694 --> 00:08:56.029
We found the owner.

00:08:56.113 --> 00:08:58.367
It's one of the second-years
on next year's council.

00:08:58.450 --> 00:09:00.581
[AYASAKI] Remi's relieved
we figured it out.

00:09:00.664 --> 00:09:01.708
[YOSHIKAWA]
Huh?

00:09:01.791 --> 00:09:04.045
You'll find Sakura
in line for the cake buffet!

00:09:04.129 --> 00:09:06.383
Cram school before we eat cake.
[sighs]

00:09:06.466 --> 00:09:08.470
[giggling]

00:09:08.555 --> 00:09:10.224
Is she okay, do you think?

00:09:10.809 --> 00:09:12.103
[ISHIKAWA]
She's been in la-la land

00:09:12.186 --> 00:09:13.480
for a hot minute now.

00:09:13.565 --> 00:09:14.734
Just leave her be.

00:09:14.817 --> 00:09:15.944
I was laughing

00:09:16.028 --> 00:09:17.488
'cause Hori switched
with you-know-who,

00:09:17.573 --> 00:09:18.407
then Remi and Kono

00:09:18.490 --> 00:09:21.496
-did the same thing!
-I'm not your punching bag.

00:09:21.581 --> 00:09:22.415
[gasps]

00:09:23.459 --> 00:09:25.589
I'm excited
for the cooking class today!

00:09:25.672 --> 00:09:28.928
-Ay, that's what's up, bro?
-Ooh, yes!

00:09:29.012 --> 00:09:29.930
[ISHIKAWA]
What is this?

00:09:30.014 --> 00:09:31.141
-[gasps]
-Huh?

00:09:31.809 --> 00:09:33.270
[YOSHIKAWA]
Trading places gets tricky

00:09:33.354 --> 00:09:34.690
when nature calls.

00:09:34.774 --> 00:09:36.443
And what about baths?

00:09:36.527 --> 00:09:37.946
Come back, Yoshikawa.

00:09:38.030 --> 00:09:39.407
Join the sane side.

00:09:39.909 --> 00:09:41.453
What about the restroom, though?

00:09:41.537 --> 00:09:43.583
[ISHIKAWA]
The restroom? What about it?

00:09:43.666 --> 00:09:46.171
It's rough on your kidneys
if you hold it in too long.

00:09:46.254 --> 00:09:47.674
Just go when you got to go.

00:09:48.384 --> 00:09:51.014
This question's more complex
than you comprehend.

00:09:51.098 --> 00:09:52.559
[ISHIKAWA]
Say what?

00:09:55.398 --> 00:09:56.567
Don't you ever call me Kyoko,

00:09:56.651 --> 00:09:58.320
'cause it would be creepy
and uncomfortable.

00:10:00.408 --> 00:10:05.084
-[YOSHIKAWA] Kyoko. Kyoko!
-[cringing]

00:10:05.167 --> 00:10:06.629
We're here for homework,
not to goof off,

00:10:06.713 --> 00:10:08.550
so I'm going to go buy
some report paper.

00:10:08.633 --> 00:10:10.219
Have a good trip.

00:10:10.302 --> 00:10:12.599
While you're there,
get some pencil lead!

00:10:12.683 --> 00:10:15.146
-[HORI] Okay!
-[door sliding]

00:10:26.502 --> 00:10:27.462
Huh?

00:10:27.546 --> 00:10:28.464
[slams]

00:10:28.548 --> 00:10:30.719
[YOSHIKAWA] I forgot to ask
for more red pens!

00:10:30.802 --> 00:10:31.637
[gasps]

00:10:34.894 --> 00:10:35.729
Aah.

00:10:36.522 --> 00:10:38.484
-[thudding]
-[whimpers]

00:10:41.072 --> 00:10:43.368
I didn't think anyone else
was in here with me.

00:10:43.452 --> 00:10:45.498
Oh. Um, well.

00:10:45.582 --> 00:10:47.335
-I'm sorry.
-No harm done.

00:10:47.418 --> 00:10:49.005
I just walked in
as Hori was leaving.

00:10:51.886 --> 00:10:53.515
[YOSHIKAWA]
This book is cold.

00:10:54.349 --> 00:10:55.894
-[YANAGI] Huh?
-Ah...

00:10:55.977 --> 00:10:57.271
I was just talking to mysel--

00:11:01.864 --> 00:11:03.033
[breathes]

00:11:03.116 --> 00:11:05.079
It feels that way
because your hands are warm.

00:11:06.999 --> 00:11:08.335
[whimpers]

00:11:09.922 --> 00:11:11.049
[YOSHIKAWA]
When the back of his knuckles

00:11:11.132 --> 00:11:13.053
brushed mine,

00:11:13.136 --> 00:11:16.059
I realized just how cold
Yanagi's hands are.

00:11:18.898 --> 00:11:20.359
-[footsteps]
-[ISHIKAWA] Hm?

00:11:21.737 --> 00:11:23.365
Yo. Do you finish your report?

00:11:23.448 --> 00:11:25.620
-[gasps] Huh?
-[YOSHIKAWA] My hands are cold.

00:11:25.704 --> 00:11:28.125
Real cold! Super-duper-cold!

00:11:28.208 --> 00:11:29.419
Huh?

00:11:30.462 --> 00:11:32.008
-[gasps]
-Feel warm enough to me.

00:11:32.091 --> 00:11:33.636
Then again, I'm freezing.

00:11:33.720 --> 00:11:36.391
Hey! That was not an invitation
to get grabby!

00:11:36.474 --> 00:11:38.478
Huh?

00:11:38.563 --> 00:11:39.732
You are such a pain!

00:11:39.815 --> 00:11:41.026
-What'd you expect me to do?
-[YOSHIKAWA muffled]

00:11:41.569 --> 00:11:43.155
[grunts]
At least Yanagi's gentle

00:11:43.238 --> 00:11:45.492
when he touches me,
unlike somebody!

00:11:45.577 --> 00:11:47.914
Are you invoking
a "no touchie" rule with me?

00:11:47.998 --> 00:11:50.127
That isn't even close
to what I said!

00:11:50.210 --> 00:11:52.674
-You're such a pain!
-Be gentle!

00:11:52.758 --> 00:11:54.093
Like, why is that?

00:11:54.177 --> 00:11:56.097
You are giving me
the biggest headache right now!

00:11:56.181 --> 00:11:57.934
-Not even kidding!
-[YOSHIKAWA] Wait!

00:11:58.018 --> 00:12:00.481
I thought you were kidding,
Toru!

00:12:00.565 --> 00:12:02.068
-[sighs]
