[FEMALE STUDENT 207C] He mouthed
"Rot in hell, ugly cows!"

00:14:09.488 --> 00:14:11.952
[FEMALE STUDENT 207C] Who does
that nosey nobody think he is?

00:14:12.913 --> 00:14:14.248
[MIYAMURA]
So,

00:14:14.332 --> 00:14:16.461
