how it feels,

00:14:33.829 --> 00:14:35.248
but someone
with your friend group

00:14:35.332 --> 00:14:36.627
could never relate!

00:14:36.710 --> 00:14:39.090
♪

00:14:39.173 --> 00:14:40.677
It just took time.

00:14:40.760 --> 00:14:41.929
It's not like I went around

00:14:42.012 --> 00:14:43.808
