And you'll be the winner.

00:14:58.963 --> 00:15:01.635
But, does winning
even have a point?

00:15:01.719 --> 00:15:03.639
I figured you'd want to win.

00:15:03.723 --> 00:15:04.558
I don't care!

00:15:06.854 --> 00:15:07.689
[sighs]

00:15:08.273 --> 00:15:11.446
