00:17:04.881 --> 00:17:06.259
[SAWADA]
Yeah! They do!

00:17:06.342 --> 00:17:07.845
-[YOSHIKAWA] Mm-hm.
-In a nutshell,

00:17:07.929 --> 00:17:08.764
