00:17:47.382 --> 00:17:48.552
[FEMALE STUDENT 207G]
Any suggestions

00:17:48.635 --> 00:17:49.554
for where to post this?

00:17:49.638 --> 00:17:50.931
I'd say the bulletin board,

00:17:51.015 --> 00:17:52.643
if we'd thought
to reserve any space.

