00:18:03.791 --> 00:18:05.335
-[SHIMODA] Really?
-[SAWADA] Recruiting for clubs

00:18:05.418 --> 00:18:06.963
seems like quite the challenge.

00:18:14.311 --> 00:18:16.065
-I never knew 'til now.
-[giggles]

