00:19:07.502 --> 00:19:08.587
[SENGOKU]
Is it even unlocked?

00:19:09.506 --> 00:19:10.674
[grunts]

00:19:10.758 --> 00:19:11.760
-[SAWADA] I'll take it down!
-[grunts]

00:19:11.843 --> 00:19:13.054
[SAWADA]
Stand aside, Prez!

00:19:13.137 --> 00:19:15.058
